data.description: Never-ending VIEWS and Country Living at it's finest!  From this beautifully updated brick home you will enjoy one of the most breathtaking views with a business benefit of 3 established rental cabins at your doorstep (4th one in progress). Possibilities are endless whether for an equestrian property, mini-farm or wedding venue. Don't dream any longer.  The main house offers 5BR/3BA which includes 2 master bed/bath, open floor plan, wood floor throughout, walk-in closets, laundry hook ups upstairs and downstairs, etc. There are 2 barns on the property. One with horse stalls and tack room. The rental cabins are 1BR/1BA, two of the cabins have additional lofts. Seller will offer TURN-KEY!
